```
numpy==1.14.2                  # Math library for array operations
opencv-contrib-python==3.4.0.12  # OpenCV with extra modules (face recognition)
```

`opencv-contrib-python` (not just `opencv-python`) is needed because the LBPH face recognizer lives in the `contrib` module.

